Type: Package
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Tools for Local Instrumental Variables (LIV) Analysis
Description: Provides functions to perform Local Instrumental Variables analysis with continuous instruments, including residualization, data filtering, LIV computation, bootstrapping, and diagnostic plotting.
